bm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073290/extras/4a82f9d0489f3ac838d62fdf7014fea0.mp4?t=1769879135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make friends! Each new friend might have something worthwhile to help you on your adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073290/extras/64e2b1144cfd6b36ad3b79fb8fa1aaea.poster.avif?t=1769879135\" width=500 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073290/extras/64e2b1144cfd6b36ad3b79fb8fa1aaea.webm?t=1769879135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073290/extras/64e2b1144cfd6b36ad3b79fb8fa1aaea.mp4?t=1769879135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unlock new movement options to help reach different areas of the world and complete new quests!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073290/extras/71c4207a666a55b6cfb3241364c8ecb8.poster.avif?t=1769879135\" width=500 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073290/extras/71c4207a666a55b6cfb3241364c8ecb8.webm?t=1769879135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073290/extras/71c4207a666a55b6cfb3241364c8ecb8.mp4?t=1769879135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Navigate a small and interconnected world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>You play as an adorable frog</strong><br></li><li><strong>Swing</strong> and <strong>jump</strong> over platforming challenges!<br></li><li><strong>Collect</strong> fireflies to unlock new <strong>abilities</strong>!<br></li><li><s